<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>LiquiLink | A Link-in-bio builder</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Create stunning link-in-bio page in minutes, free for starters, paid for pros."
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css"
      integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
    <style>
      .landing-stack {
        padding: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem) 0 5rem;
      }

      .landing-narrow {
        max-width: 42rem;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }

      .landing-stack .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
      }

      .landing-stack h1 {
        margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
        line-height: 1.1;
        font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 5vw, 2.35rem);
      }

      .landing-stack h1 span {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 0.4rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .landing-stack .hero-text {
        margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .landing-stack .landing-actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .landing-narrow .landing-actions {
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }

      .landing-preview-wrap {
        width: min(1040px, 100%);
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      }

      .landing-preview-wrap iframe {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        border: 0;
        display: block;
        pointer-events: none;
        user-select: none;
      }

      .landing-preview-caption {
        margin: 0 auto 2.75rem;
        padding: 0 0.25rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .landing-prose {
        max-width: 42rem;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .landing-prose h2 {
        margin: 2.25rem 0 0.75rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      .landing-prose h2:first-child {
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      .landing-prose p {
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .landing-prose p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="landing-page">
    <main class="container landing-stack">
      <div class="landing-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Free to start</p>
        <h1>
          LiquiLink
          <span>Make your link-in-bio feel premium.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-text">
          One short form, one polished page, one shareable URL like
          <span class="mono">https://liquilink.in/your-name</span>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="landing-actions landing-narrow">
        <% if (currentUser) { %>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/dashboard">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-table-columns" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          Go to my dashboard
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/form.html">Create new portfolio</a>
        <form action="/logout" method="POST">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-ghost">Logout</button>
        </form>
        <% } else { %>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          Create your account
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/login">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-right-to-bracket" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          Log in to dashboard
        </a>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <div class="landing-preview-wrap" aria-label="Example preview of a published page">
        <iframe
          src="/atharv-raj-sharma"
          title="Example LiquiLink page (non-interactive preview)"
          loading="lazy"
          tabindex="-1"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
      <p class="landing-preview-caption landing-narrow">
        Above is an example of a real page created with LiquiLink after someone
        submits the form. The preview is read-only here: you cannot click or edit
        it on the home page; it is only meant to show what visitors will see.
      </p>

      <div class="landing-prose">
        <h2 id="what-is-liquilink">What is LiquiLink?</h2>
        <p>
          LiquiLink is a link-in-bio builder and lightweight portfolio host. You
          describe yourself once—projects, socials, contact—and we turn that into
          a fast, good-looking page you can put in every bio where your name
          appears.
        </p>

        <h2 id="about-the-product">About the product</h2>
        <p>
          There is no heavy CMS and no separate design tool to learn. You fill out
          a guided form, see how the page will look, and use your dashboard to
          update your public link when your details change. The free tier is meant
          to be easy to try; pro options are there when you want more control.
        </p>

        <h2 id="why-use-it">Why people use it</h2>
        <p>
          Many people juggle different links across profiles—work samples in one
          place, contact in another, older bios that never get updated. Visitors
          get a scattered picture, and you maintain several spots instead of one.
        </p>
        <p>
          LiquiLink gives you a single page that reads clearly and stays easier to
          keep current, so the link you share is the one that actually represents
          you.
        </p>
        <p>
          In practice you submit the form once, receive one unique link, and reuse
          that same link everywhere you want people to find you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
